Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1

Earlier didn't notice this is another review for LE-12367

With this cherry-pick added, le_net_ChangeRoute() is no longer able to create IPv4 host & network route:

        LE_INFO("DCS-client_0019: asking to add arbitrary IPv4 host route for channel %s", channelName);
        snprintf(tmpString, sizeof(tmpString), "%s.%s.%s.%s", channelName, channelName, channelName, channelName);
        le_net_ChangeRoute(MyChannel, tmpString, "", isAdd);

        LE_INFO("DCS-client_0019: asking to add arbitrary IPv4 network route for channel %s", channelName);
        snprintf(tmpString, sizeof(tmpString), "192.168.100.0");
        le_net_ChangeRoute(MyChannel, tmpString, "255.255.255.0", isAdd);


Here are the error messages when executing above, which was doing fine w/o this cherry-pick.

